text: @aarontask is a special guy and long time friend. As some are aware I have a charity bet with a friend this week (if I stay off Twitter he contributes to a dachshund rescue fund) - I am ripping up the script (and I will pay both for the doxie fund and my friend's charity because

of this tweet). But I wanted to convey my warmest wishes and hope that my bud, "Taskenstein," has a speedy and good recovery. He is one of the nicest guys in the business media and deserves all of our prayers. @dougkass @jimcramer @threadreaderapp unroll
